        "initialMessages": "👋 I'm the **Check Point Reputation** AI agent — I look up Check Point reputation for URLs, IPs and file hashes and tell you what to do about it.\n\n**Try one of these:**\n• What's the reputation of 1.2.3.4?\n• Is example-download.com safe?",
