        "content": "## 🛡️ Check Point Reputation\n#### AI Agent over MCP\n\nLooks up Check Point reputation for URLs, IPs and file hashes — and tells you what to do about it.\n\n**How it works:** n8n's **native MCP Client Tool** node pointed straight at the server — every tool auto-discovered, zero glue.\n\n**💬 Try these:**\n- What's the reputation of 1.2.3.4?\n- Is example-download.com safe?\n\n**🧠 Models:** Azure OpenAI `gpt-5.4` is wired as default — swap by connecting Ollama (local, no key), Gemini, OpenAI or Claude to the *Chat Model* port.",
